  <!-- EN: The void has awoken. The gate is open. The darkness of the void rushes into our reality, manifested from a vast mind of endless rage. -->
  <Gleaming.extraQuestDescription>虛空甦醒了。大門已經開啟。虛空的黑暗湧入了我們的現實，從無盡憤怒的巨大心靈中顯現出來。</Gleaming.extraQuestDescription>
  <!-- EN: Level 4: Awakened -->
  <Gleaming.levelInspectText>等級4 ：甦醒</Gleaming.levelInspectText>
